4","tid":514481,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T16:40:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1月1有全日早餐咪又係排晒隊去食<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>求下你 求下你地 唔好食呀 出面大把選擇點解要用廿幾蚊係m記食<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢。 去大快活  KFC mos burger 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n落樓下想食炒蛋同薯餅唔去老麥唔通特登搭車去食kfc咩，仲要kfc個炒蛋難食到我食開垃圾都唔屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想人去食kfc同mos嘅唔係唔得，但佢啲分店唔算多唔似得老麥梗有一間喺左近咁方便，好難怪人邊屌邊食喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c009daab3b0b9e949a58861cea4a0027657d607","tid":514481,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T06:04:49.000Z","msg":"有朋友做過麥記 真係分開兩包<br />\n一包槌一包翼炸，證明麥當勞真係好仆街"},{"pid":"fb8569fffb9eabfe2e58a0795b871dd60c951bb8","tid":514481,"uid":61529,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T07:26:49.000Z","msg":"大快活質素真係好過大家樂 琴日去食啲阿姐服務都幾好"},{"pid":"97badc9be54c34b79c1655af04093d97f11cfb56","tid":514481,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T18:17:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}